Comment: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:26.24,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I was gazing at the drifting clouds.
Comment: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:33.29,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(0,250)}I was feeling the changes in the sky's color.
Comment: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:41.34,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\be1}As we stop walking,
