Comment: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:55.73,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just as you scan with the fingers you spread,
Comment: 0,0:22:55.73,0:23:04.36,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I search for the one thing that never changes.
Comment: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:11.95,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}Let there be a torch in the hand you reach out.
Comment: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:19.50,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\be1}There'll be a small sign leading to tomorrow.
Comment: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:27.05,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The word you said that day...
Comment: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:34.56,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\be1}...still echoes in my head, and let's make it an oath.
Comment: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:39.81,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I will continue going with it.
